[17.409889, "o", "Error: Governance error: Secret detected: API Key Assignment [HARD-MANDATORY]\r\n\r\n  At: line 4: api_***************************************************************4yZ\"\r\n  Rule (govern.json): code_quality.no_secrets = \"hard\"\r\n\r\n  Help:\r\n  - Never hardcode secrets in source code\r\n  - Use environment variables instead\r\n\r\n  Example:\r\n    ✗ Blocked:\r\n      API Key Assignment = \"api_***************************************************************4yZ\"\"\r\n    ✓ Allowed:\r\n      import os\r\n      key = os.environ[\"YOUR_KEY_NAME\"]\r\n      \r\n        In NAAb:\r\n          let key = env.get_var(\"YOUR_KEY_NAME\")\r\n\r\n"]
